  "name": "Rite: Corrupt Item",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/equipment/neck/amulet-round-engraved-blue.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 5th level Occultist</em></p>\n<p>You use a dark and secret rite to corrupt a non-magical item, causing it to become a cursed magic item. While any creature other than you is in possession of this item, they are under the effect of&nbsp;bane.</p>\n<p>Select one of the following for the item's magical property (the item must be of a type of item that could be the magical item selected):&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bag of tricks,</li>\n<li>brooch of shielding,</li>\n<li>goggles of night,</li>\n<li>lantern of revealing,&nbsp;or&nbsp;</li>\n<li>staff of the python&nbsp;(you can ignore attunement restrictions of this item).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>When you change rites, you can reselect this rite to destroy the item and create a new item.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This is not automated.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
